<p>For the convenience of our repetitive visitors we are introducing the Translit Bookmarklet feature. Now you can save your time and call up our translit converter via a single mouse click!</p>
<p>Translit Bookmarklet is a button placed on your browser's Bookmarks Toolbar or Links Bar. Translit button launches the Russian translit converter in a separate pop-up window and does not affect the website you are currently surfing on.</p>
<p>To use the bookmarklet from this site follow these steps:</p>
<ol>
<li>Drag the bookmarklet <a class="bml" href="javascript:void%20window.open('http://translit.cc/mini','_blank','width=800,height=480,resizable=yes,toolbar=no,status=no,scrollbars=no,menubar=no,location=no')">TRANSLIT</a> to your Bookmarks Toolbar or Links Bar.</li>
<li>While viewing a page you want to use the translit converter on, click the <a class="bml" href="javascript:void%20window.open('http://translit.cc/mini','_blank','width=800,height=480,resizable=yes,toolbar=no,status=no,scrollbars=no,menubar=no,location=no')">TRANSLIT</a> bookmarklet from your Bookmarks Toolbar.</li>
</ol>

